{"id":634530,"date":[{"year":1982,"month":6,"day":9}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"266","ytitle":"","mtitle":"纪念赤石暴动四十周年","ftitle":"","authors":["蔡园"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔡园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"救亡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东南火燧半沉沦*，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慷慨悲歌出中原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芒履宵征传号角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌寇夜遁失惊魂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*南方八省游击健儿，深入江南敌后开辟抗日民主根据地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皖变"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皖南血火带硝烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鏖战兼旬众山间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千古奇冤一叶落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饮痛回首四十年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤暴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤石狂飚动地歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拼搏崇溪震山河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里闵赣任驰骋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"武夷山上复扬戈!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祭扫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长眠虎山*四十秋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾眶热泪忆同俦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一束鲜花清明祭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松柏掩映山更幽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*国民党特务在虎山庙先后屠杀我七十余烈士。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悼念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"武夷年年飞白雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜宇声声更断肠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧血长虹染赤石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深山日暮吊小杨*!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*杨瑞年(女)烈士昂首就义，身负七弹犹高呼共产党万岁，甚为壮烈。"}]}